high_descs: Move forward to the kitchen island, then turn right and go around the kitchen island, then turn right to go to the sink.
Pick up the potato from the counter in front of the sink.
Turn left to face the counter with the microwave on it
Open the microwave, put the potato inside and cook it, then take the potato out.
Turn right to face the sink.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm potato in the sink.
